Package: libreoffice-kde4
Architecture: %OOO_ARCHS%
Depends: libreoffice-core (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: ${kde-iconset-dep}
Suggests: kmail, konqueror, kleopatra | kgpg
Section: kde
Enhances: libreoffice
Replaces: libreoffice-core (= 1:4.3.0~beta1-1), libreoffice-kde (<< 1:6.1.0~alpha1-1)
Breaks: libreoffice-kde (<< 1:6.1.0~alpha1-1)
Description: office productivity suite -- KDE 4 integration
 LibreOffice is a full-featured office productivity suite that provides
 a near drop-in replacement for Microsoft(R) Office.
 .
 This package contains the KDE plugin for drawing LibreOffices widgets with
 KDE/Qt and a KDEish File Picker when running under KDE.
 You can extend the functionality of this by installing these packages:
 .
  * konqueror / kmail

